### state

- `lifecycle`: Status (init, active, drifting, archived)
- `decay_status`: Temporal relevance indicator (stable, decaying, obsolete)
- `federation_link`: Path in the federated architecture (e.g., GAIA-AIR/NODE-31B)

### xai

